title: WSJF - Scaled Agile Framework
excerpt: Weighted Shortest Job First (WSJF) is a prioritization model used to sequence work for maximum economic benefit. In SAFe, WSJF is estimated as the relative cost of delay divided by the relative job duration.

title: The Algorithms That Make Instacart Roll
excerpt: Instacart crunches petabytes daily to predict what will be on grocery shelves and even how long it will take to find parking
